project_descr: SUPPORT TO THE ESTABLISHMENT OF REGIONAL PLANNING COMMISSION

outputs.output_descr: The objective this IP is to lay the framework for the institutional development of the newly established Regional Planning Commission (RPC) under the auspices of the Office of the Prime Ministry.  The main outputs of the project is to design and propose an administrative and organizational structure for the Regional Planning Commission as per its mandate (Law No 26/2010) as well as develop a full-fledged Project Document to operationalize the organizational structure recommended by the IP Team

project_title: support to the establis. of regional planning commission
